OL,3,CMan admits to stealing #27,000 from
OL,4,Chis grandmother
OL,6,FA man from Workington has admitted to
OL,7,Fstealing #27,000 from his grandmother.
OL,9,FKevin Teasdale, 38, pleaded guilty to
OL,10,Fone count of theft at Carlisle Crown
OL,11,FCourt on Friday 3 May 2024.
OL,13,FHe, admitting that he stole #27,000
OL,14,Fcash belonging to his grandma last
OL,15,Fmonth.
OL,17,FHe could receive a prison sentence for
OL,18,Fthe crime.
